tags: GDHHSHSJDKF THIS IS DEKU AS A VILLAIN LET’S BE REAL
body:
villain deku headcanons

- aizawa: ‘did you do your homework’ deku, a fucking liar: ‘yeah all of it’

- he takes a chocolate bar from the store and forgets to pay for it. that’s his supervillain origin story

- todoroki: ‘what’s the baddest thing you’ve ever done’

- deku, who stole his neighbour’s newspaper once in 6th grade and cried about it every day since: ‘i’m a real stinky bastard man shouto. you just wouldn’t understand’

- deku: ‘i’m the worst. i’m a monster. they don’t know the darkness inside because it’s swallowed me whole and none of them could ever handle it and-‘

- ochako: ‘what did you do’ deku, choked: ‘forgot to say thank you to the bus driver’

- all might: ‘….so you’ve done it. you’ve become evil’

- deku: ‘everything you taught me was a lie’ all might: ‘no. i trusted you. we could’ve been great’

- deku standing in the shadows: ‘i don’t believe you’ all might tearing up: ‘i loved you like a son. come back to the light young midoriya’

- deku turning away: ‘NO. i can’t come back from this’ all might wailing: ‘weuhhhwuheuwubdubdub’

- deku screaming: ‘i didn’t return that library book and now it’s too late for me!!!!!!!!’

title: Burden to Bear Update!
body:
Chapter 13!

This Chapter: Internships begin!

DadMight AU in which Izuku is actually All Might’s son, and knows it, but All Might hasn’t allowed the information to go public. Izuku knows why it’s always been a secret, but there is some part of him that wonders if there is more to it than just protecting him and his mom. Izuku is believed to be quirkless before receiving One for All, but actually isn’t.

Or read from the beginning!
